      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRANT KEEPING (1) recorded his best time this course and distance last start, taking a Grade 4/5 in 29.64 by 0.8 lengths. Happy to have him on top again. DENNIS KEEPING (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (29.35) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 516m. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. In sparkling form and expected to measure up again. VALEDICTORIAN (2) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (29.86) at this track. Solid winning record at this trip. Has good speed and a low draw is a big help. Leading chance. TRACEY TARO (7) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.",
